"title": "8425: evangelism, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8425: evangelism, nature of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Evangelism focuses on the proclaiming of the good news of the coming of the kingdom of God in Christ, including the forgiveness of sins and the hope of eternal life, through the death and resurrection of Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>Evangelism as the proclamation of good news</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:7\">ISA 52:7</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:15\">MRK 16:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:31\">2SA 18:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs7:9\">2KI 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:9\">ISA 40:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:27\">ISA 41:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:15\">NAM 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:7\">ACT 14:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:15\">ACT 14:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:15\">ROM 10:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:16\">ROM 15:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:7\">1TI 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:11\">2TI 1:11</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ as the focus of evangelism</h2>\n<h3>The gospel message is revealed by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:11-Gal1:12\">GAL 1:11–1:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:25-Rom16:26\">ROM 16:25–16:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:15-Gal1:16\">GAL 1:15–1:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:3-Eph3:6\">EPH 3:3–3:6</a></p>\n<h3>The gospel message centres on Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:1\">MRK 1:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:8\">EPH 3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:19\">LUK 1:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:10\">LUK 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:16-Luke3:18\">LUK 3:16–3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:20\">ACT 11:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:9\">ROM 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:4\">2CO 4:4</a></p>\n<h3>The announcement of God's kingdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:31\">ACT 28:31</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:14\">MAT 24:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:14-Mark1:15\">MRK 1:14–1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:43\">LUK 4:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:1\">LUK 8:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:2\">LUK 9:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:12\">ACT 8:12</a></p>\n<h3>God's promises are fulfilled in Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18-Luke4:19\">LUK 4:18–4:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:2\">ISA 61:1–61:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:3-Matt11:5\">MAT 11:3–11:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:20-Luke7:22\">LUK 7:20–7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:42\">ACT 5:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:35\">ACT 8:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:22\">ACT 9:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:32-Acts13:33\">ACT 13:32–13:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:2-Rom1:4\">ROM 1:2–1:4</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's death and resurrection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:3-1Cor15:4\">1CO 15:3–15:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:22-Acts2:24\">ACT 2:22–2:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:15\">ACT 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:18\">ACT 17:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:14\">1CO 15:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:23\">1CO 1:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:8\">2TI 2:8</a></p>\n<h3>The announcement of God's salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:16-Rom1:17\">ROM 1:16–1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:10\">PSA 40:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:2-Ps96:3\">PSA 96:2–96:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:23-1Chr16:24\">1CH 16:23–16:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:21\">1CO 1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:1-1Cor15:2\">1CO 15:1–15:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:13\">EPH 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:13-2Thess2:14\">2TH 2:13–2:14</a></p>\n<h3>The call to repentance for the forgiveness of sins</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:47\">LUK 24:47</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:17\">MAT 4:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:41\">MAT 12:41</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:32\">LUK 11:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:4\">MRK 1:4</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:2\">MAT 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:3\">LUK 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:38\">ACT 2:38</a></p>\n<h3>The announcement of peace with God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:36\">ACT 10:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:17-Eph2:18\">EPH 2:17–2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:15\">EPH 6:15</a></p>\n<h2>Evangelism and miracles</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:23\">MAT 4:23</a></strong> <em>Miracles are part of the gospel proclamation, demonstrating that the kingdom of God has come</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:4-1Cor2:5\">1CO 2:4–2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:35\">MAT 9:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:7-Matt10:8\">MAT 10:7–10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:6\">LUK 9:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:20\">LUK 11:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:18-Rom15:19\">ROM 15:18–15:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:5\">1TH 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:3-Heb2:4\">HEB 2:3–2:4</a></p>",
